y avoid the use of products containing ginkgo biloba.', 'Synergism', 'Patients should consult a healthcare provider before taking any herbal or alternative medicine.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/153453/', '', 'St. John''s Wort, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Tryptophan, Esketamine', 'Rivastigmine, Galantamine, Aducanumab, Memantine, Tacrine', 1767369485);
